net.uoit.rmd.security

Class JobServerSecurityManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.SecurityManager
      • net.uoit.rmd.security.JobServerSecurityManager

  • public class JobServerSecurityManager
extends SecurityManager
    Provides security on a per-thread basis to sandbox jobs. Only the class that executes jobs has the right to enable and disable the security.
